cz.cvut.felk.cig.jcop.result
Interface Result

All Known Implementing Classes:
SimpleResult
public interface Result

Result contains all information about Solver.run() run of a solver.

Result can contain multiple entries for the same problem or algorithm, entries are not required to be unique at all.

Entries in result has 3 main parts - its algorithm, its problem and resulting data (time, number of optimizations etc).
